          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 60 of a 12-week money program. The script targets two things: the fear of providing too little for children, and the weight of carrying financial anxiety that has its roots in an earlier generation. The reframe moves toward abundance rippling forward, a new normal of financial ease, started here.",
            "type": "text"
          }
